@meirkay
#repost 
・・・
With the rise of Anti-Semitism I took to the streets to stand for peace, for understanding and connection. 

I had many open and honest conversations which only reminded me how we have more in common than we are lead to believe. 

Love and respect one another.

 Let's make this world that much more of a peaceful and brighter, together.

node.text: I love Conan. I don’t care who knows it. He’s always been game to go all the fucking way…In comedy and kindness. What an amazing honor to be on the farewell show. Much love to him and the whole incredible @teamcoco crew and family. Can’t wait to see what the next chapter brings! #ConanAtLargo

node.text:
@meirkay
#repost 
・・・
With the rise of Anti-Semitism I took to the streets to stand for peace, for understanding and connection. 

I had many open and honest conversations which only reminded me how we have more in common than we are lead to believe. 

Love and respect one another.

 Let's make this world that much more of a peaceful and brighter, together.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jack Black on May 26, 2021. May be an image of 5 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Devastating news. Kevin is gone. Way too soon. Beautiful soul. So many great memories. Heartbroken. Sending love to his family and the whole School of Rock community.
